    <description>This container serves as a repository for the matrix table containing various rates and units. The matrix table will subsequently be utilized in MR calculation following its association with supplemental rent.
The Ratio Table acts as a central location to define headers for tables associated with Performance Restoration maintenance reserves. Each table defines a rate based on the ratio of Hours/Cycles and any necessary Derate adjustments. Notably, a single Ratio Table can be used efficiently to manage rates for multiple Maintenance Reserve funds.
